---
title: Nan's Creamy Chicken Fettuccine with Parmesan & Hidden Leek
description: This saucy creation uses a creamy tomato sauce to coat fettuccine, with chunks of tender chicken and flavoursome Parmesan. Add thinly
sliced leek that melts into the sauce and baby spinach that gently wilts when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.

